	column Web_Grounded_Signal = ```
			
			    VAR resType    = LOWER('Chat + Agent Interactions (Audit Logs)'[AccessedResource_Type])
			    VAR siteUrl    = LOWER('Chat + Agent Interactions (Audit Logs)'[AccessedResource_SiteUrl])
			    VAR isInternal = CONTAINSSTRING(siteUrl, "sharepoint.com") || CONTAINSSTRING(siteUrl, ".onmicrosoft.com")
			    RETURN
			        IF(
			            resType = "websearchquery"
			            || resType IN {"external","http"}
			            || (resType = "http://schema.skype.com/hyperlink" && NOT isInternal),
			            "Web Grounded",
			            "Not Web Grounded"
			        )
			```
